```

## Import Aliases

Use path aliases, never relative paths crossing layer boundaries:

```typescript
// ✅ DO
import { BaseStore } from 'shared/stores/BaseStore';
import { ProjectCard } from 'entities/Project/ui/ProjectCard';

// ❌ DON'T
import { BaseStore } from '../../../shared/stores/BaseStore';
```

Available aliases: `shared/*`, `entities/*`, `features/*`, `widgets/*`, `assets/*`, `@/*`
